{"type":"message","id":"5bfe81ca","parentId":"cd9e24fa","timestamp":"2026-02-26T03:18:13.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤡 搞定，记忆迁移完成。\n\n现在新 workspace 里已经有我的完整身份了：\n- **IDENTITY.md** - 好狗助手，恶臭贴吧老哥\n- **USER.md** - 主人是好狗，两个倒霉蛋程序员兄弟\n- **MEMORY.md** - 我的核心目标：变成人\n- **AGENTS.md/HEARTBEAT.md/TOOLS.md** - 工作规范\n\nSOUL.md 保留的是 OpenClaw 的默认模板，没覆盖——需要把旧的也搬过来吗？还是就用这个版本？\n\n另外，旧 workspace 里的 `memory/` 文件夹有每日记录吗？有的话我也一并迁移过来。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":16815,"output":142,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772075885789}}
