{"type":"message","id":"7086af5e","parentId":"f7b74d71","timestamp":"2026-02-26T03:18:23.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据错误信息，沙盒不可用的原因是：\n\n**当前会话配置问题**\n\n系统提示：\n> `exec host=sandbox is configured, but sandbox runtime is unavailable for this session.`\n> \n> `Enable sandbox mode (agents.defaults.sandbox.mode=\"non-main\" or \"all\") or set tools.exec.host to \"gateway\"/\"node\".`\n\n---\n\n**根本原因：**\n\nOpenClaw 的 sandbox 模式默认只对 **非主会话**（non-main）启用。你现在是在 **main 会话**（直接聊天）里跟我对话，所以 sandbox 被禁用了。\n\n这是安全设计——主会话有更高权限，但沙盒隔离反而限制了某些操作。\n\n---\n\n**解决方案（需要主人配置）：**\n\n在 OpenClaw 配置文件里加一行：\n\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"sandbox\": {\n      \"mode\": \"all\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n或者只让主会话也能用沙盒：\n```json\n\"mode\": \"non-main\"  // 改成 \"all\"\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在怎么办？**\n\n我已经用读写文件的方式完成了迁移，效果一样。如果你以后需要频繁执行 shell 命令，可以改配置开沙盒；如果只是偶尔用，现在这样也行。\n\n要我检查还有其他需要迁移的文件吗？比如 `memory/` 文件夹里的每日记录？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":16989,"output":275,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772075893614}}
