{"type":"message","id":"3c893dfd","parentId":"6301cde3","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:30:03.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经写好了 DuckDuckGo 搜索服务器，但现在有个问题：**OpenClaw 原生不支持 MCP 协议**，也不支持自定义 HTTP 工具。\n\n让我总结一下现状和可行方案：\n\n---\n\n## 现状\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| DuckDuckGo 搜索服务器 | ✅ 已写好 (`tools/ddg_search_server.py`) |\n| OpenClaw MCP 支持 | ❌ 不支持 |\n| OpenClaw 自定义工具 | ❌ 不支持直接添加 |\n\n---\n\n## 可行方案\n\n### 方案 1：启动 DDG 服务器 + 用 `web_fetch` 调用（现在就能用）\n\n1. **手动启动服务器**（需要你自己在终端运行）：\n   ```bash\n   cd D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tools\n   python ddg_search_server.py\n   ```\n\n2. **我用 `web_fetch` 调用**：\n   ```\n   GET http://127.0.0.1:18795/search?q=关键词\n   ```\n\n但这需要你保持那个终端窗口开着。\n\n---\n\n### 方案 2：修改 GoodDog 代码（推荐）\n\n既然你的 GoodDog 系统已经有完整的工具架构，而且已经有 `WebSearchTool` 实现了，**直接用 GoodDog 就行**：\n\n```bash\ncd D:\\gooddog\npython start.py\n```\n\nGoodDog 的 `web_search` 工具就是 DuckDuckGo，完全免费。\n\n---\n\n### 方案 3：等 OpenClaw 更新\n\nOpenClaw 未来可能会支持 MCP 或自定义工具，但现在没有。\n\n---\n\n## 我的建议\n\n**直接用 GoodDog**。你花了时间写那个系统，它已经完美支持 DuckDuckGo 搜索了。OpenClaw 这边我可以继续用 `web_fetch` 做网页抓取，但搜索这块 GoodDog 更自由。\n\n要我帮你启动 GoodDog 吗？还是你想先试试方案 1，手动跑那个 DDG 服务器？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":54270,"output":413,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54683,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772083675364}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b7f0a02","parentId":"3c893dfd","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:46:53.921Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-26 13:46 GMT+8] cursor帮你写好了ddg的mcp， 在 OpenClaw 里怎么用确保启用了 mcporter skill在 OpenClaw 的 skills 里把 mcporter 打开（若默认已带就不用改）。让 agent 用 ddgsearchAgent 会通过 mcporter 调用 MCP，例如：mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search query=\"你想搜的内容\"或：mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search \"关键词\" numResults=5 mode=detailed若 agent 工作目录里没有 config若执行 mcporter 时提示找不到配置，可以让 agent 带 config 路径再试，例如：mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search query=xxx --config D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\config\\mcporter.json"}],"timestamp":1772084813915}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8dfac5d","parentId":"6b7f0a02","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:47:13.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了！Cursor 已经帮你写好了 MCP 服务器，现在需要配置 OpenClaw 使用 mcporter skill 来调用它。\n\n让我检查一下当前的 skill 配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:59","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\npm-global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\skills\\mcporter\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":54866,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54937,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772084813919}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c5ce711","parentId":"f8dfac5d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:47:13.959Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:59","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: mcporter\ndescription: Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure, auth, and call MCP servers/tools directly (HTTP or stdio), including ad-hoc servers, config edits, and CLI/type generation.\nhomepage: http://mcporter.dev\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"📦\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"mcporter\",\n              \"bins\": [\"mcporter\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install mcporter (node)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# mcporter\n\nUse `mcporter` to work with MCP servers directly.\n\nQuick start\n\n- `mcporter list`\n- `mcporter list <server> --schema`\n- `mcporter call <server.tool> key=value`\n\nCall tools\n\n- Selector: `mcporter call linear.list_issues team=ENG limit:5`\n- Function syntax: `mcporter call \"linear.create_issue(title: \\\"Bug\\\")\"`\n- Full URL: `mcporter call https://api.example.com/mcp.fetch url:https://example.com`\n- Stdio: `mcporter call --stdio \"bun run ./server.ts\" scrape url=https://example.com`\n- JSON payload: `mcporter call <server.tool> --args '{\"limit\":5}'`\n\nAuth + config\n\n- OAuth: `mcporter auth <server | url> [--reset]`\n- Config: `mcporter config list|get|add|remove|import|login|logout`\n\nDaemon\n\n- `mcporter daemon start|status|stop|restart`\n\nCodegen\n\n- CLI: `mcporter generate-cli --server <name>` or `--command <url>`\n- Inspect: `mcporter inspect-cli <path> [--json]`\n- TS: `mcporter emit-ts <server> --mode client|types`\n\nNotes\n\n- Config default: `./config/mcporter.json` (override with `--config`).\n- Prefer `--output json` for machine-readable results.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772084833954}}
