{"type":"message","id":"2d9d09a8","parentId":"f9628288","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:11:31.449Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.exec:71","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ddgsearch\n\n  /**\n   * Perform a web search using DuckDuckGo and receive detailed results including titles, URLs, and\n   * summaries.\n   *\n   * @param query Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\n   * @param numResults? Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\n   * @param mode? Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results\n   *              (includes Description).\n   */\n  function web-search(query: string, numResults?: number, mode?: \"short\" | \"detailed\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\"\n          },\n          \"numResults\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\",\n            \"default\": 3,\n            \"minimum\": 1,\n            \"maximum\": 20\n          },\n          \"mode\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results (includes Description).\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"short\",\n              \"detailed\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"short\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using IAsk.ai. Retrieves comprehensive, AI-generated responses based on web\n   * content. Supports different search modes (question, academic, forums, wiki, thinking) and detail\n   * levels (concise, detailed, comprehensive). Ideal for getting well-researched answers to complex\n   * questions.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for\n   *              comprehensive AI-generated responses.\n   * @param mode? Search mode to use. Options: \"question\" (general questions), \"academic\"\n   *              (scholarly/research), \"forums\" (community discussions), \"wiki\" (encyclopedia-style),\n   *              \"thinking\" (deep analysis). Default is \"question\".\n   * @param detailLevel? Level of detail in the response. Options: \"concise\" (brief), \"detailed\"\n   *                     (moderate), \"comprehensive\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\n   */\n  function iask-search(query: string, mode?: \"question\" | \"academic\" | \"forums\" | \"wiki\" | \"thinking\", detailLevel?: \"concise\" | \"detailed\" | \"comprehensive\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for comprehensive AI-generated responses.\"\n          },\n          \"mode\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Search mode to use. Options: \\\"question\\\" (general questions), \\\"academic\\\" (scholarly/research), \\\"forums\\\" (community discussions), \\\"wiki\\\" (encyclopedia-style), \\\"thinking\\\" (deep analysis). Default is \\\"question\\\".\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"question\",\n              \"academic\",\n              \"forums\",\n              \"wiki\",\n              \"thinking\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"question\"\n          },\n          \"detailLevel\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Level of detail in the response. Options: \\\"concise\\\" (brief), \\\"detailed\\\" (moderate), \\\"comprehensive\\\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"concise\",\n              \"detailed\",\n              \"comprehensive\"\n            ]\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using Monica AI. Returns AI-generated responses based on web content.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question.\n   */\n  function monica-search(query: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"The search query or question.\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search(query: \"value\", numResults: 3, mode: \"short\")\n\n  3 tools · 4715ms · STDIO npx -y @oevortex/ddg_search@latest"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5663,"aggregated":"ddgsearch\n\n  /**\n   * Perform a web search using DuckDuckGo and receive detailed results including titles, URLs, and\n   * summaries.\n   *\n   * @param query Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\n   * @param numResults? Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\n   * @param mode? Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results\n   *              (includes Description).\n   */\n  function web-search(query: string, numResults?: number, mode?: \"short\" | \"detailed\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\"\n          },\n          \"numResults\": {\n            \"type\": \"integer\",\n            \"description\": \"Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\",\n            \"default\": 3,\n            \"minimum\": 1,\n            \"maximum\": 20\n          },\n          \"mode\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results (includes Description).\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"short\",\n              \"detailed\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"short\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using IAsk.ai. Retrieves comprehensive, AI-generated responses based on web\n   * content. Supports different search modes (question, academic, forums, wiki, thinking) and detail\n   * levels (concise, detailed, comprehensive). Ideal for getting well-researched answers to complex\n   * questions.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for\n   *              comprehensive AI-generated responses.\n   * @param mode? Search mode to use. Options: \"question\" (general questions), \"academic\"\n   *              (scholarly/research), \"forums\" (community discussions), \"wiki\" (encyclopedia-style),\n   *              \"thinking\" (deep analysis). Default is \"question\".\n   * @param detailLevel? Level of detail in the response. Options: \"concise\" (brief), \"detailed\"\n   *                     (moderate), \"comprehensive\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\n   */\n  function iask-search(query: string, mode?: \"question\" | \"academic\" | \"forums\" | \"wiki\" | \"thinking\", detailLevel?: \"concise\" | \"detailed\" | \"comprehensive\");\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for comprehensive AI-generated responses.\"\n          },\n          \"mode\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Search mode to use. Options: \\\"question\\\" (general questions), \\\"academic\\\" (scholarly/research), \\\"forums\\\" (community discussions), \\\"wiki\\\" (encyclopedia-style), \\\"thinking\\\" (deep analysis). Default is \\\"question\\\".\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"question\",\n              \"academic\",\n              \"forums\",\n              \"wiki\",\n              \"thinking\"\n            ],\n            \"default\": \"question\"\n          },\n          \"detailLevel\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"Level of detail in the response. Options: \\\"concise\\\" (brief), \\\"detailed\\\" (moderate), \\\"comprehensive\\\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"concise\",\n              \"detailed\",\n              \"comprehensive\"\n            ]\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using Monica AI. Returns AI-generated responses based on web content.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question.\n   */\n  function monica-search(query: string);\n      {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"query\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"description\": \"The search query or question.\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"query\"\n        ]\n      }\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search(query: \"value\", numResults: 3, mode: \"short\")\n\n  3 tools · 4715ms · STDIO npx -y @oevortex/ddg_search@latest","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772086291442}}
{"type":"message","id":"58a53be2","parentId":"2d9d09a8","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:12:14.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！ddgsearch 有 **3 个工具**：\n1. `web-search` - DuckDuckGo 搜索\n2. `iask-search` - AI 搜索（IAsk.ai）\n3. `monica-search` - Monica AI 搜索\n\n但刚才调用失败了，可能是网络问题。让我再试一次，用英文关键词："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:72","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search \"Stephen Chow\" numResults=3 mode=detailed","host":"gateway"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":58982,"output":116,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59098,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772086291449}}
