{"type":"message","id":"58a8ec76","parentId":"c46c9ade","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:14:25.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我的错误信息：\n\n```\nError executing tool 'web-search': Search failed for \"Stephen Chow\": canceled\n```\n\n和\n\n```\nError searching IAsk: IAsk search failed for \"周星驰是谁\": connect ETIMEDOUT 108.160.169.54:443\n```\n\n---\n\n**根本原因：网络超时**\n\nMCP 服务器（`@oevortex/ddg_search@latest`）在尝试连接 DuckDuckGo 和 IAsk 时超时了。这说明：\n\n1. **DuckDuckGo 被墙或限流** - 你的网络环境无法直接访问\n2. **IAsk.ai 同样被墙** - IP `108.160.169.54:443` 连接超时\n\n---\n\n**不是我的问题，是网络问题**\n\n- mcporter ✅ 正常工作\n- ddgsearch MCP ✅ 已注册\n- 工具调用 ✅ 能执行\n- 网络连接 ❌ 超时\n\n---\n\n**解决方案**\n\n要我启动我之前写的 **本地 DDG 服务器** 吗？那个是直连 DuckDuckGo，如果 DuckDuckGo 本身被墙，可能也需要代理。\n\n或者你有 HTTP/HTTPS 代理的话，告诉我地址，我可以配置给 mcporter 用。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":60131,"output":255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60386,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772086455063}}
