{"type":"message","id":"087edadb","parentId":"6024fcb4","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:20:27.509Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.process:82","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  /**\n   * Perform a web search using DuckDuckGo and receive detailed results including titles, URLs, and\n   * summaries.\n   *\n   * @param query Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\n   * @param numResults? Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\n   * @param mode? Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results\n   *              (includes Description).\n   */\n  function web-search(query: string, numResults?: number, mode?: \"short\" | \"detailed\");\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using IAsk.ai. Retrieves comprehensive, AI-generated responses based on web\n   * content. Supports different search modes (question, academic, forums, wiki, thinking) and detail\n   * levels (concise, detailed, comprehensive). Ideal for getting well-researched answers to complex\n   * questions.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for\n   *              comprehensive AI-generated responses.\n   * @param mode? Search mode to use. Options: \"question\" (general questions), \"academic\"\n   *              (scholarly/research), \"forums\" (community discussions), \"wiki\" (encyclopedia-style),\n   *              \"thinking\" (deep analysis). Default is \"question\".\n   * @param detailLevel? Level of detail in the response. Options: \"concise\" (brief), \"detailed\"\n   *                     (moderate), \"comprehensive\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\n   */\n  function iask-search(query: string, mode?: \"question\" | \"academic\" | \"forums\" | \"wiki\" | \"thinking\", detailLevel?: \"concise\" | \"detailed\" | \"comprehensive\");\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using Monica AI. Returns AI-generated responses based on web content.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question.\n   */\n  function monica-search(query: string);\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search(query: \"value\", numResults: 3, mode: \"short\")\n\n  3 tools · 11115ms · STDIO npx -y @oevortex/ddg_search@latest\n\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quick-gulf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"ddgsearch\n\n  /**\n   * Perform a web search using DuckDuckGo and receive detailed results including titles, URLs, and\n   * summaries.\n   *\n   * @param query Enter your search query to find the most relevant web pages.\n   * @param numResults? Specify how many results to display (default: 3, maximum: 20).\n   * @param mode? Choose 'short' for basic results (no Description) or 'detailed' for full results\n   *              (includes Description).\n   */\n  function web-search(query: string, numResults?: number, mode?: \"short\" | \"detailed\");\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using IAsk.ai. Retrieves comprehensive, AI-generated responses based on web\n   * content. Supports different search modes (question, academic, forums, wiki, thinking) and detail\n   * levels (concise, detailed, comprehensive). Ideal for getting well-researched answers to complex\n   * questions.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question to ask. Supports natural language questions for\n   *              comprehensive AI-generated responses.\n   * @param mode? Search mode to use. Options: \"question\" (general questions), \"academic\"\n   *              (scholarly/research), \"forums\" (community discussions), \"wiki\" (encyclopedia-style),\n   *              \"thinking\" (deep analysis). Default is \"question\".\n   * @param detailLevel? Level of detail in the response. Options: \"concise\" (brief), \"detailed\"\n   *                     (moderate), \"comprehensive\" (extensive). Default is null (standard response).\n   */\n  function iask-search(query: string, mode?: \"question\" | \"academic\" | \"forums\" | \"wiki\" | \"thinking\", detailLevel?: \"concise\" | \"detailed\" | \"comprehensive\");\n\n  /**\n   * AI-powered search using Monica AI. Returns AI-generated responses based on web content.\n   *\n   * @param query The search query or question.\n   */\n  function monica-search(query: string);\n\n  Examples:\n    mcporter call ddgsearch.web-search(query: \"value\", numResults: 3, mode: \"short\")\n\n  3 tools · 11115ms · STDIO npx -y @oevortex/ddg_search@latest\n\n","name":"mcporter list"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772090427502}}
