{"type":"message","id":"f96d1d96","parentId":"cc759b8e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T07:26:15.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到了！Cursor 的指南和我测试的结果一致。\n\n让我把这个使用指南记录下来，方便以后自动选择："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:91","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","content":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## MCP 搜索工具使用指南\n\n### 推荐：ddgs_search（多后端，国内更稳）\n\n**优先使用此工具**，走好狗那套多后端（auto + Bing 回退），网络不稳时更容易出结果。\n\n```bash\n# 基本搜索\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"你想搜的内容\"\n\n# 指定结果数（默认10，最大20）\nmcporter call ddgs_search.web_search query=\"关键词\" max_results=10\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ 多引擎自动切换（ddgs auto + Bing 回退）\n- ✅ 国内网络更稳定\n- ✅ 支持中英文搜索\n- ✅ 返回标题、URL、摘要\n\n---\n\n### 备用：ddgsearch.monica-search（AI 生成答案）\n\n当 ddgs_search 失败时，可用 Monica AI 搜索作为备用。\n\n```bash\nmcporter call ddgsearch.monica-search query=\"关键词\"\n```\n\n**特点：**\n- ✅ AI 生成综合答案\n- ✅ 带引用来源\n- ⚠️ 不如 ddgs_search 稳定\n\n---\n\n### 已弃用：ddgsearch.web-search / iask-search\n\n这两个工具在国内网络环境下经常超时/被墙，不推荐使用。\n\n```bash\n# ❌ 不推荐，容易失败\nmcporter call ddgsearch.web-search query=\"...\"\nmcporter call ddgsearch.iask-search query=\"...\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 其他工具\n\nSkills define _how_ tools work. This file is for _your_ specifics — the stuff that's unique to your setup.\n\n### Cameras\n\n- living-room → Main area, 180° wide angle\n- front-door → Entrance, motion-triggered\n\n### SSH\n\n- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin\n\n### TTS\n\n- Preferred voice: \"Nova\" (warm, slightly British)\n- Default speaker: Kitchen HomePod\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":64755,"output":521,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65276,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772090753251}}
